<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/racist-attacks-and-border-militarization-intensify-as-coronavirus-spreads/">Racist Attacks and Border Militarization Intensify as Coronavirus Spreads</a>
</h2>
